rComments: Très bon prof! Cours facile pour un cours de 4ième année. Il enrégistre des viédos (un PP et sa voix) et le publie avant le cours. Le cours sert uniquement a répondre aux question (pas nécessaire d'y assister si tu comprend tout). Contenue est clair et facile. Un projet d'équipe. N'utilise pas Respondus. Prend ce prof!

Amazing guy that really want people to succeed in business but his class are not well prepared, unclear criteria for works and exams. He barely replies to emails so you have to catch him after class if you have questions ...

He is very passionate about the class and really cares if students understand what he's teaching. That could also be seen as annoying if someone in your class doesn't understand a very easy concept he will go through it over and over again to make sure that one student understands. Other than that, has a good sense of humour, good prof.
Nice prof, explains the material well. His grading criteria is not super clear though, but will answer your questions if you ask him.
